# {{grammar}} A [[word]] that can be used to refer to a [[person]], [[place]], [[thing]], [[quality]], or [[idea]]; a part of [[speech]] ([[w:Part of speech|Wikipedia article on parts of speech]]). It can serve as the subject or object of a verb. For example, ''a table'' or ''a computer''.

